BT 1 0 0 1 0 135 Tm -0.049421 Tw 12 TL /F1 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg (We present the formal derivation of the Wike Scaling Law C = C_0 ) Tj /F3 9 Tf (exp\(-alpha ) Tj /F1 9 Tf (gamma_eff\) directly from the Lindblad master) Tj T* 0 Tw (equation for open quantum systems. Beginning from first principles of quantum mechanics, we show that coherence --) Tj T* (defined as the magnitude of off-diagonal density matrix elements -- decays exponentially under decoherence with a) Tj T* (universal functional form. We identify the critical decoherence rate gamma_c = 1/alpha at which the vitality function) Tj T* (V\(gamma\) = C_0 ) Tj /F3 9 Tf (gamma ) Tj /F1 9 Tf (exp\(-alpha * gamma\) achieves its maximum, corresponding to the phase boundary between) Tj T* (frozen order, living criticality, and collapsed incoherence. From 1,050,000 Jarzynski equality simulations, we extract the) Tj T* (anomalous correction exponent 2.59, which we identify as 1 + 1/nu where nu = 0.6298 is the 3D Ising correlation length) Tj T* (exponent, verified by conformal bootstrap to 0.2%. We prove universality of the Wike transition across 13,810,660 total data) Tj T* (points spanning superconducting qubits, IBM quantum hardware at 15 mK, human body temperature regulation, chronic) Tj T* (pain wind-up, immune discrimination, fever dynamics, adverse childhood experience dose-response, artificial intelligence) Tj T* (behavioral collapse, civilizational survival, and the cosmological constant. The Wike Scaling Law is a 3D Ising phase) Tj T* (transition in the coherence order parameter.) Tj T* ET
